			<!-- ======================== SECTION 7: LOCALES vs GLOBALES comparación ======================== -->
			<section class="section section-hidden" id="sec-scope">
				<div class="section-inner">
					<div class="anim-item text-center mb-10" style="--delay: 0ms">
						<h2 class="font-retro text-4xl md:text-6xl uppercase tracking-tight">
							Locales <span class="opacity-30">vs</span> Globales
						</h2>
						<p class="text-sm opacity-50 mt-2">Y el misterio del <strong>shadowing</strong>: cu&aacute;ndo una variable oculta a otra</p>
					</div>

					<div class="anim-item code-block text-xs mb-6" style="--delay: 150ms">
<span class="code-type">int</span> <span class="code-var" style="color:#fcd34d">x</span> = <span class="code-number">100</span>; <span class="code-comment">// GLOBAL x</span><br><br>
<span class="code-keyword">void</span> <span class="code-func">miFuncion</span>() &lbrace;<br>
<span style="padding-left:16px"><span class="code-type">int</span> <span class="code-var" style="color:#a5f3fc">x</span> = <span class="code-number">5</span>; <span class="code-comment">// LOCAL x — OCULTA a la global</span></span><br>
<span style="padding-left:16px"><span class="code-func">printf</span>(<span class="code-string">"%d"</span>, <span class="code-var" style="color:#a5f3fc">x</span>); <span class="code-comment">// imprime 5, no 100</span></span><br>
&rbrace; <span class="code-comment">// la local x desaparece acá</span><br><br>
<span class="code-type">int</span> <span class="code-func">main</span>() &lbrace;<br>
<span style="padding-left:16px"><span class="code-func">printf</span>(<span class="code-string">"%d"</span>, <span class="code-var" style="color:#fcd34d">x</span>); <span class="code-comment">// imprime 100 (la global)</span></span><br>
<span style="padding-left:16px"><span class="code-func">miFuncion</span>();              <span class="code-comment">// imprime 5</span></span><br>
<span style="padding-left:16px"><span class="code-func">printf</span>(<span class="code-string">"%d"</span>, <span class="code-var" style="color:#fcd34d">x</span>); <span class="code-comment">// sigue siendo 100</span></span><br>
&rbrace;
					</div>

					<div class="flex gap-6 split-grid">
						<div class="flex-1 anim-item type-card" style="--delay: 300ms">
							<p class="text-xs opacity-50 mb-1" style="color:#a5f3fc">LOCAL (cyan)</p>
							<p class="text-sm">Existe solo dentro de su bloque. Tiene prioridad sobre la global del mismo nombre dentro de ese scope. Cuando el bloque termina, desaparece del stack.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex-1 anim-item type-card" style="--delay: 400ms; border-color: rgba(251,191,36,0.25)">
							<p class="text-xs opacity-50 mb-1" style="color:#fcd34d">GLOBAL (amber)</p>
							<p class="text-sm">Visible desde cualquier funci&oacute;n. Si una funci&oacute;n tiene una local del mismo nombre, la global queda <strong>oculta (shadowed)</strong> dentro de esa funci&oacute;n.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

