							Par&aacute;metros Nominales y Efectivos
						</h2>
						<p class="text-sm opacity-50 mt-2">Definici&oacute;n vs llamada. Placeholder vs valor real.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
						<!-- Nominales -->
						<div class="anim-item split-col" style="--delay: 150ms">
							<h3 class="font-retro text-2xl mb-1">PAR&Aacute;METROS NOMINALES</h3>
							<p class="text-xs opacity-60 mb-4">Los de la DEFINICI&Oacute;N &mdash; son placeholders, variables locales</p>

							<div class="code-block text-sm mb-4">
<span class="code-type">int</span> <span class="code-func">calcular</span>(<span class="code-type">int</span> <span style="border-bottom:2px solid var(--primary); color:var(--primary)">base</span>, <span class="code-type">int</span> <span style="border-bottom:2px solid var(--primary); color:var(--primary)">altura</span>) &lbrace;<br>
<span style="padding-left:16px"><span class="code-keyword">return</span> <span style="color:var(--primary)">base</span> * <span style="color:var(--primary)">altura</span>;</span><br>
&rbrace;
							</div>

							<div style="display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap">
								<span class="param-badge-nominal">base</span>
								<span class="param-badge-nominal">altura</span>
							</div>
